# =============================================================
# Microsoft Foundry — SmartClaims Agent Configuration
# =============================================================
# INSTRUCTIONS:
#   1. Copy this file:  cp .env.example .env
#   2. Fill in YOUR values below
#   3. Never commit .env to version control
